data.description: Don't miss your chance to see this wonderful 3 bedroom/ 2 bath ranch located on a quiet street. As you walk in, the large living area with real hardwood floors provides ample space for family and entertainment.  Large kitchen with stainless steel appliances and separate dining room.  Primary bedroom has a full bathroom and large closet.  The backyard provides a large covered patio and a fenced in yard that backs up to greenspace and the walking trail!  Call your realtor today to go see this home before its gone! Home being sold as-is
